t/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/Qu%C3%BD-D%E1%BA%ADu-th%E1%BB%A7-h%E1%BA%A1-giai-N%E1%BA%A1i-Vi%C3%AAn-%C6%AFng-Ngh%E1%BB%87-Lan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-%C6%AFng-B%E1%BB%99-Th%C3%BAc-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-%C6%AFng-Lo%E1%BA%A1i-Thanh-Chi-%C6%AFng-Th%C3%B4ng-t%C3%B2ng/poem-Y7ZPhBO2kzL37-JhpkFRMg">Quý Dậu thủ hạ giai Nại Viên Ưng Nghệ, Lan Đình Ưng Bộ, Thúc Đồng Ưng Loại, Thanh Chi Ưng Thông tòng Bình Định tỉnh án sát sứ Thiếp Thiết, Phù Cát huyện doãn Thái Văn Chánh phóng Linh Phong cổ tự - 癸酉首夏偕柰園膺藝蘭亭膺蔀叔同膺蘱青之膺蔥從平定省按察使䀡沏符吉縣尹蔡文正訪靈峰古寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Thu%E1%BA%A5n-Kh%C3%A2m/Thi%C3%AAn-B%C3%ACnh-s%C6%A1n/poem-CrkPNETORjAdBnI-FGBJiQ">Thiên Bình sơn - 天平山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Thu%E1%BA%A5n-Kh%C3%A2m/author-2_TKpTo9LIhei08LC-iYaw">Tô Thuấn Khâm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-H%E1%BB%93ng-V%E1%BB%8Bnh/Th%E1%BB%A7-tu%E1%BA%BF/poem-YJEgNI42GwRsTMeaGKD46A">Thủ tuế - 守歲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-H%E1%BB%93ng-V%E1%BB%8Bnh/author-E6a5e7SOI8-d6_k05ZXmwg">Nguyễn Phúc Hồng Vịnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Thu%C3%BD-Hoa-s%C6%A1n/poem-JyokTsUCXU7xNWft5ka9IQ">Thuý Hoa sơn - 翠花山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-H%E1%BB%A3p/V%C4%83n-thi%E1%BB%81n-k%C3%BD-Gi%E1%BA%A3-%C4%90%E1%BA%A3o/poem-5FAFUDFyyOkqMTUtvBmf5A">Văn thiền ký Giả Đảo - 聞蟬寄賈島</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-H%E1%BB%A3p/author-vs3gFjAvih8Xq3PRsiAJTg">Diêu Hợp</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
